    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. 6 factors appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate RH index agreement within 8.4% across all operating points; acceptance criterion RH < 1 satisfied at all conditions. Pressure rise and WSS validation provide mechanistic corroboration. Uncertainty quantification performed for RH index and WSS validation results. Note: uncertainty characterization for the pressure rise validation result relied on qualitative assessment of manufacturing variability rather than structured probabilistic analysis; this is considered acceptable at MRL 2 given the secondary role of pressure rise in the hemolysis decision chain. Overall credibility sufficient to support the COU decision at Medium assurance level.",
